   PHILADELPHIA-ORCHESTRA (Undated) _ Arts in America: The
Philadelphia Orchestra marks its centennial with 20th-century
music. By Anthony Tommasini.
</P>
<P>
   STUDENT-OSCAR (New York) _ A student filmmaker, Keiko Ibi, gets
an Oscar nomination for her short documentary, ``The Personals:
Improvisations on Romance in the Golden Years.'' By Felicia R. Lee.
</P>
