<TEXT>
<P>
   The following is a description of the NASCAR page available as
part of The New York Times Syndicate's PageExpress service. The
page will be available by 5 p.m. EST on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
   DALE JARETT: NASCAR driver Dale Jarrett goes for three straight
victories at Darlington Raceway as the Winston Cup circuit moves to
South Carolina's landmark racing venue.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: NASCAR-ITEMS: Odds/ends package.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: WINSTON-NOTES: Winston/Busch notes package.
</P>
</TEXT>
