<HEADLINE>
AMERICA'S SWEET ON HONEY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By BEVERLY BUNDY 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Pooh Bear's cupboards can hardly be bare these days. It seems
