<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-17 17:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4160 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PRIVACY-0318-COX     03-17 0708
