<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    ADVISORY
 &HT;    Resending to change ''percent'' to ''percentage points'' in last
graph
 &HT;    
 &HT;    WORK IS NO FAMILY VACATION
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
