security, working conditions and relationships with co-workers and
bosses, according to a survey released today (Thursday).
</P>
<P>
   While job satisfaction is high in the current economy - 88
percent are satisfied with their job, 54 percent are ``very''
satisfied - 95 percent of the adults surveyed said they are
